“How long, my fellow- soldiers, must we obey a small and despicable set of centurions‘? How long continue slaves to a wretched band of military trib- unes? If we mean to redress our grievances, what time so fit as the present, when the new emperor is not yet settled on the throne? Relief may now be obtained, either by remonstrances‚ or sword in hand.
